          "text" : "Discussion",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "content" : [
            {
              "inlineContent" : [
                {
                  "text" : "An error indicating that the current test or test case has been",
                  "type" : "text"
                },
                {
                  "text" : " ",
                  "type" : "text"
                },
                {
                  "text" : "cancelled. The testing library does not treat this error as a test",
                  "type" : "text"
                },
                {
                  "text" : " ",
                  "type" : "text"
                },
                {
                  "text" : "failure.",
                  "type" : "text"
                }
              ],
              "type" : "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name" : "Throws",
          "style" : "note",
          "type" : "aside"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "The testing library runs each test and each test case in its own task.",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "When you call this function, the testing library cancels the task",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "associated with the current test:",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "code" : [
            "@Test func `Food truck is well-stocked`() throws {",
            "  guard businessHours.contains(.now) else {",
            "    try Test.cancel(\"We're off the clock.\")",
            "  }",
            "  \/\/ ...",
            "}"
          ],
          "syntax" : "swift",
          "type" : "codeListing"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "If the current test is a parameterized test function, this function",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "instead cancels the current test case. Other test cases in the test",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "function are not affected.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "If the current test is a suite, the testing library cancels all of its",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "pending and running tests.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "If you have already cancelled the current test or if it has already",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "finished running, this function throws an error to indicate that the",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "current test has been cancelled, but does not attempt to cancel the test a",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "second time.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "content" : [
            {
              "inlineContent" : [
                {
                  "text" : "If the current task is not associated with a test (for",
                  "type" : "text"
                },
                {
                  "text" : " ",
                  "type" : "text"
                },
                {
                  "text" : "example, because it was created with ",
                  "type" : "text"
                },
                {
                  "identifier" : "https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/swift\/task\/detached(name:priority:operation:)-795w1",
                  "isActive" : true,
                  "type" : "reference"
                },
                {
                  "text" : ")",
                  "type" : "text"
                },
                {
                  "text" : " ",
                  "type" : "text"
                },
                {
                  "text" : "this function records an issue and cancels the current task.",
                  "type" : "text"
                }
              ],
              "type" : "paragraph"
            }
          ],
